{"type": "article", "id": 14061, "title": "大长腿算什么，现在流行把奥迪A4穿在身上", "description": "车模的新战袍。", "date": "2015-08-27T09:13:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 165, "name": "时装"}, {"id": 154, "name": "奥迪"}, {"id": 1014, "name": "英特尔"}, {"id": 15080, "name": "Anouk Wipprecht"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607125113ykJUqhng1HbNpCVv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t擅于玩转时尚与科技的荷兰设计师 <span>Anouk Wipprecht </span>日前发布了四款奥迪 <span>A4 </span>系列时装，通过服饰来展示整车技术与机械美感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125111RbWngE213UklmOcJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125111UAbnqjJwV3NfagG2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Projection Map </span>礼服基于奥迪的虚拟座舱设计而成，在衣服上的两片护罩植入了奥迪超声波测距传感器，当人靠近到一定距离便会触发耀眼的 <span>LED </span>大灯。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071251120eSjCMHBRUQPVFIb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<span> </span> \r\n<p>\r\n\t展览还使用了大量的动态投影，使礼服看起来像是处于运动状态。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t除了智能元件的应用，<span>Wipprecht </span>还花了很多时间与奥迪 <span>A4 </span>的开发者们交流，揣摩他们的设计灵感和元素，比如奥迪 <span>A4 </span>的前部的菱形设计思路也被应用到了时装上。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141705RO312tGNhLVrZEz7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>Wipprecht </span>使用英特尔的 <span>RealSense </span>技术对模特的体型、曲线和骨骼结构进行了扫描，然后进行 <span>3D </span>设计并打印出来，打印一件礼服大约需要 <span>3 </span>天时间。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t下面这个视频可以看到具体的设计细节。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=DARqRav98RE&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=380561142_06_05_99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t作为先锋派艺术家，<span> Wipprecht </span>曾创造过许多令人印象深刻的设计作品，比如与英特尔合作的 <span>3D </span>打印智能连衣裙 <span>Synapse</span>、外形酷似蜘蛛的 <span>Spider Dress </span>等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071251123YGbJBOsvhyHXpQd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}